  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_5fb90e6a52794f02be87322f3c0db626">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Collection contains the 1949 commencement program and reunion materials from 1989, 1999, 2009, and 2014, inlcuding lists of attendees, reunion booklets, and a DVD of oral histories recorded at the 2014 reunion from members associated with the class of 1949. Also includes the results of a 1959 class questionnaire.</p>  </scopecontent>
