id="aspace_d58acd65e9a8299c4546d59f3367c0c2" label="Mixed Materials [31924113896348]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_51eac14f326c90ab80768c0935693224" parent="aspace_d58acd65e9a8299c4546d59f3367c0c2" type="folder">2</container><container id="aspace_b170e56e7c84312745136c703989b989" parent="aspace_51eac14f326c90ab80768c0935693224" type="dvd">1149</container></did><scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_893fe95418e82949f3ae9bf1c404539c"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>DVD of oral histories recorded at reunion 2014 from members associated with the Class of 1949. The DVD features Martha Coler Risch '49, Vera Farrell '49, Bill Feinberg '49, Don Sutherland '49, Martha Ohaus '47, Jerry Alpern '49, and Carl Schwarzer '49. Topics include coming to Cornell, women at Cornell, World War Two and military service, dating, exams, and other campus life.</p></scopecontent></c01></dsc>
